Package com.example.qrchive.Classes

Class ScannedCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.qrchive.Classes.ScannedCode
  • public class ScannedCode
extends java.lang.Object
    ScannedCode represents a code that has been captured and stores all the required metadata to operate on such a code.

        userDID - is the users ID.
        scannedCodeDID - is the scanned codes ID.
